{
  "id": "formatting",
  "title": "ðŸŽ¨ Advanced Document Formatting",
  "description": "Formatting is the key to creating professional and visually appealing documents in Word. This lesson covers advanced formatting techniques including text styles, paragraph formatting, and document themes.",
  "metadata": {
    "duration": "30 minutes",
    "difficulty": "Intermediate",
    "prerequisites": ["intro"]
  },
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Advanced formatting transforms plain text into professional documents. Learn how to use styles, themes, and layout tools to create visually appealing and well-structured documents."
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Learning Objectives"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "unordered",
        "items": [
          "Master Word styles and themes",
          "Create professional page layouts",
          "Use headers, footers, and page numbers",
          "Apply advanced text formatting",
          "Create and customize document sections"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Styles and Themes"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Understanding Styles"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Styles are predefined formatting combinations that ensure consistency throughout your document."
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "data": {
        "headers": ["Style Type", "Purpose", "Example"],
        "rows": [
          ["**Heading Styles**", "Create document hierarchy", "Heading 1, Heading 2, Heading 3"],
          ["**Paragraph Styles**", "Format body text", "Normal, Body Text, Quote"],
          ["**Character Styles**", "Format specific text", "Strong, Emphasis, Code"],
          ["**List Styles**", "Format lists consistently", "List Paragraph, List Bullet"]
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Applying Styles"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "ordered",
        "items": [
          "Select the text you want to format",
          "Go to the **Home** tab",
          "Choose a style from the **Styles** gallery",
          "Or use **Ctrl + Shift + S** to open the Styles pane"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Customizing Styles"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Modify existing styles or create new ones to match your document needs."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "unordered",
        "items": [
          "Right-click a style and select **Modify**",
          "Change font, size, color, and spacing",
          "Set paragraph formatting options",
          "Choose whether to update all instances"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Page Layout and Design"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Page Setup"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Control how your document appears on the page with proper margins, orientation, and size settings."
    },
    {
      "type": "table",
      "data": {
        "headers": ["Setting", "Options", "Use Case"],
        "rows": [
          ["**Page Size**", "Letter, A4, Legal, Custom", "Match paper or digital format"],
          ["**Orientation**", "Portrait, Landscape", "Optimize for content type"],
          ["**Margins**", "Normal, Narrow, Wide, Custom", "Control white space"],
          ["**Columns**", "1, 2, 3, More", "Newsletter or brochure layout"]
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Headers and Footers"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Add professional information to every page with headers and footers."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "unordered",
        "items": [
          "**Headers**: Company name, document title, date",
          "**Footers**: Page numbers, contact info, confidentiality notice",
          "**Different First Page**: Special header/footer for title page",
          "**Different Odd & Even**: Mirror layout for double-sided printing"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Page Numbers"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Automatically number pages for easy navigation and professional appearance."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "ordered",
        "items": [
          "Go to **Insert** tab > **Page Number**",
          "Choose position (top, bottom, margins)",
          "Select format (1, 2, 3 or i, ii, iii)",
          "Customize with chapter numbers if needed"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Advanced Text Formatting"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Font Effects and Advanced Options"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Go beyond basic formatting with advanced text effects and options."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "unordered",
        "items": [
          "**Text Effects**: Shadow, reflection, glow, bevel",
          "**Character Spacing**: Expand or condense text",
          "**OpenType Features**: Ligatures, stylistic sets",
          "**Advanced Typography**: Kerning, baseline shift"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Drop Caps and Special Characters"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Add visual interest with decorative elements and special characters."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "unordered",
        "items": [
          "**Drop Caps**: Large initial letters for paragraphs",
          "**Symbols**: Mathematical, currency, copyright symbols",
          "**Equations**: Insert mathematical formulas",
          "**SmartArt**: Create diagrams and charts"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Document Sections"
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Understanding Sections"
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "content": "Sections allow you to have different formatting within the same document."
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "unordered",
        "items": [
          "**Different page orientations** (portrait/landscape)",
          "**Different column layouts** (1, 2, 3 columns)",
          "**Different headers and footers**",
          "**Different page numbering** schemes"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "subheading",
      "content": "Creating Section Breaks"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "ordered",
        "items": [
          "Place cursor where you want the break",
          "Go to **Layout** tab > **Breaks**",
          "Choose section break type:",
          "  - **Next Page**: New section on new page",
          "  - **Continuous**: New section on same page",
          "  - **Even/Odd Page**: New section on even/odd page"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Practice Exercise"
    },
    {
      "type": "exercise",
      "data": {
        "title": "Create a Professional Report",
        "description": "Practice advanced formatting by creating a multi-section report with different layouts.",
        "steps": [
          "Create a new document with title page",
          "Add section break for main content",
          "Apply different headers for each section",
          "Use styles for consistent formatting",
          "Add page numbers and table of contents"
        ],
        "checklist": [
          "Title page has no page number",
          "Main content has proper headers",
          "Styles are applied consistently",
          "Page numbers appear correctly",
          "Document looks professional"
        ],
        "estimatedTime": "20 minutes",
        "difficulty": "intermediate"
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "content": "Best Practices"
    },
    {
      "type": "list",
      "data": {
        "type": "ordered",
        "items": [
          "**Use styles consistently** throughout the document",
          "**Keep formatting simple** - less is often more",
          "**Test printing** to ensure layout works on paper",
          "**Use templates** for recurring document types",
          "**Consider accessibility** with proper heading structure"
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "tip",
      "content": "Use **Format Painter** (Ctrl + Shift + C) to quickly apply formatting from one element to another."
    }
  ]
} 